      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是Education_LMS_Portal，然后进入Lobby状态。那GameStarted是主持人点击开始后才触发的？需要标注触发条件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
